2019-03-28  Robert Tiemann  <r.tiemann@ta-hifi.de>

	* Version 1.0 released.

	* Fix: Avoid file descriptor and memory leak. Frequent network
	  reconfigurations can exhaust the number of available file
	  descriptors, making our device undiscoverable on the network.

2017-07-13  Robert Tiemann  <r.tiemann@ta-hifi.de>

	* Version 0.2 released.

	* Web server: Redirect all HTTP requests on UPnP server port to the
	  local web server. This allows relative links to icons and other
	  stuff be served by a proper web server, not by us.

2015-10-01  Robert Tiemann  <r.tiemann@ta-hifi.de>

	* Version 0.1 released.

	* First release for testing.


